fermion writes "The Register reports a study that indicates that [0]iPods
and pacemakers do not get along. While there do not appear to be any long
term effects, iPods disrupt the operation of the pacemaker. It is noted
that such effects have not previously been observed as iPods do seem to
be popular with the pacemaker-wearing population."

